            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing small, efficient creatures and pump spells to quickly overwhelm the opponent and win through combat damage. With Tifa Lockhart as the commander, the goal is to play aggressive creatures like Elvish Mystic and Llanowar Elves early on to ramp into bigger threats like Kazandu Mammoth and Mossborn Hydra. Pump spells like Giant Growth and Scale Up help enhance the power of these creatures, while cards like Inkmoth Nexus provide alternate win conditions. The deck also includes land ramp spells like Crop Rotation and Utopia Sprawl to ensure a consistent mana base. Overall, the strategy revolves around building a board presence quickly and efficiently to beat down the opponent before they can stabilize."
